      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get moving? This vehicle is the ultimate blank canvas for a DIY enthusiast! While it shows heavy signs of its long journey and will need some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to return to its prime, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. Perfect for a mechanic or anyone who loves a good restoration challenge!",
